  "detailed_description": "<h1>关于我们</h1><p>欢迎奖《猫头鹰和灯塔》添加至您的愿望单<br>关注我们第一时间获得游戏最新动态<br>欢迎加入玩家QQ群唠嗑：797016716<br>新浪微博：猫头鹰和灯塔<br>问题反馈QQ：800177550</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>这里有一座灯塔，远方的旅人们，请进来留下你的故事吧！<br>游戏中你会感受到昼夜交替，需要在每个时间段出发探索森林，收集到制作木雕的材料。每个木雕都会吸引到一位有故事的客人。当他们推开灯塔的大门，迎来的将会是来自一只会说话的猫头鹰，犀利又毒舌。<br>听了他们的故事，你会选择递上一杯热茶吗？<br><br>游戏特色：<br>随着日转星移，灯塔会迎来春夏秋冬和风霜雪雨的洗礼。你可以选择暂时停留在某个季节或天气中，沉浸于这静谧的景色。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591500/extras/ee7e2647f03bc0b58d3eff7bcaf2a18d.poster.avif?t=1626170795\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591500/extras/ee7e2647f03bc0b58d3eff7bcaf2a18d.webm?t=1626170795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591500/extras/ee7e2647f03bc0b58d3eff7bcaf2a18d.mp4?t=1626170795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>探索森林、收集材料、购买配方，你将配方和材料一起交给老人约翰，他制作的木雕会指引在森林里迷失徘徊的人们前来灯塔。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591500/extras/f31133faca224fe6f4e70498978f6406.avif?t=1626170795\" width=616 height=347 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591500/extras/7287f02b020b7b59ed84255cacc8b829.avif?t=1626170795\" width=616 height=348 /></span><br>这里有只活了1400年的毒舌猫头鹰，每天怀着忧伤和孤独，却仍然强行装酷。它的名字叫做“伯爵”，确实是一只猫头鹰。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591500/extras/8cf6361e7adf172c9785cef62b818c9d.avif?t=1626170795\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>灯塔接待了无数形形色色的访客。他们带来离奇的故事，独立成章，又相互关联。宿命和梦想，疯狂和悲伤；光怪陆离，人间百态。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591500/extras/1e6e3b086a75f9b6dbd35014f2cb5752.avif?t=1626170795\" width=616 height=348 /></span><br><br><strong>谨此游戏，献给许许多多孤独的人们。</strong>",
